		<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content mw-content-ltr" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><p>This instrument is made for the VEMD hardware made by Sim Innovations, and simulates the VEMD software for the Airbus Helicopters H120 / Eurocopter EC120. The hardware consist of two so called lanes, lane 1 and lane 2. The top lane, lane 1, moves to lane 2 in case lane 1 is turned off or fails.
</p>
